						<summary>

						<p>Slab paved on the floor in the <hi rend="italic">mukha-maṇḍapa</hi> of the Chauḍēśvari temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1475 Khara, Māgha śu. 15, Thursday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records that names Pallavali Yallappa and the members of his family who are stated to be ardent devotees of Chauḍēśvari of Nandavaram.</p>						

