<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrī gaṇādhipatayēnamaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī vijayābhyuda 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ya śālivāhana śakavaraṣaṁbbulu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1475 Agunēṭi 
<lb n="3"/>khara saṁvatsara māgha śu 15 guruvāraṁ naṁddavaraṁ 
<lb n="4"/>cavuḍēśvaraṁmmaku śubhamastu pallavali yalla 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ppa komāruḍu rāmaṁnna Ārāmaṁnna ko 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>māḷlu sūrappa paṭṭābhi laccaya gurva 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ppa Ā paṭṭābhi komāruḍu śītārāmuḍu 
<lb n="8"/>Ā sūrappa komāḷlu subbaya yallama 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rsu sārvakālamaṁdu tana hṛdaya daḷaka 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rṇnikāmadhyamaṁdu baṁgāru puṣpāla 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>tō pūjacēsuṁnnu yēkāgracittulai bha 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ktulai vuṁnnāru <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear>bhoṭla</unclear> 
</p>

